title: #54 - Vsauce3 (Jake Roper)
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we are joined by the illustrious Jake Roper, aka Vsauce3! We cover the creative process, Beme, space travel, and of course- sounding. Jake Roper aka Vsauce 3 is a YouTuber and director who makes fascinating videos exploring science, technology, and fictional worlds.
